---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
		<h1
			class="mb-12 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
		>
			About Me
		</h1>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-16">
			<article class="lg:col-span-2">
				<div class="space-y-10 text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
					<div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
						<p class="font-medium text-neutral-900 italic">
							I operate at the intersection of data, strategy, and servant leadership.
						</p>
					</div>

					<p>
						My mission is to build systems that bring order to chaos and remove barriers to success.
					</p>

					<p>
						I design roadmaps and I build the engine to drive it. Whether I'm evaluating programs, designing solutions in Salesforce to fix barriers for scholars and staff, building and strengthening partnerships, or leading teams through strategic change, my focus is simple: cut through the complexity and make the strategy actually work in the real world.
					</p>

					<div class="my-8">
						<h3 class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400">
							How I Operate
						</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-4">
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span
									class="mr-3 mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"
								></span>
								<span
									><strong>Evidence over Intuition:</strong> Good intentions don't solve problems; clean,
									valid data should guide problem framing, alternatives for action, and evaluation of
									our work.</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span
									class="mr-3 mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"
								></span>
								<span
									><strong>Leadership is Service:</strong> Strategy fails without execution, and
									execution requires trusting relationships. I lead by removing barriers and building
									capacity so my teams can do their best work.</span
								>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<span
									class="mr-3 mt-1.5 h-2 w-2 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-primary"
								></span>
								<span
									><strong>Discipline is Non-Negotiable:</strong> As a professional, husband, dad, and an athlete, I subscribe to the belief that consistency and standards drive
									results. Keep showing up.</span
								>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-8">
						<h3 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-neutral-900">The Real Work</h3>
						<p class="mb-8">
							I am originally from Louisiana and currently live in Washington, D.C. I am fortunate to have
							married my best friend and favorite person, adopted the greatest rescue on the planet
							(Franklin), and spent the last two years with George—the coolest kid in The District. He
							makes me the proudest dad alive. When I am not in the office, I am training to improve
							fitness, coaching others to do the same, reading a book or learning something new, or
							exploring the outdoors with my family!
						</p>

						<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
							<div
								class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-sm transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
							>
								<img
									src="/liza_preston.JPG"
									alt="Preston with Liza"
									class="h-48 w-full object-cover grayscale transition-all duration-500 hover:grayscale-0"
								/>
							</div>
							<div
								class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-sm transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
							>
								<img
									src="/family_halloween.jpg"
									alt="Family Halloween photo"
									class="h-48 w-full object-cover grayscale transition-all duration-500 hover:grayscale-0"
								/>
							</div>
							<div
								class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-sm transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]"
							>
								<img
									src="/Franklin.JPEG"
									alt="Franklin"
									class="h-48 w-full object-cover grayscale transition-all duration-500 hover:grayscale-0"
								/>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>

			<aside class="lg:col-span-1">
				<div
					class="sticky top-24 border-t border-neutral-300/70 bg-white/60 p-8 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm lg:border-l lg:border-t-0 lg:pl-8"
				>
					<div class="space-y-8">
						<div>
							<p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">
								Current Role
							</p>
							<p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-neutral-900">
								Chief Strategy & <br />Analytics Officer
							</p>
							<p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">DC-CAP</p>
						</div>

						<div>
							<p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">
								Core Focus
							</p>
							<ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-base font-medium text-neutral-800">
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<span class="mr-2 text-primary">→</span> Program Strategy
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<span class="mr-2 text-primary">→</span> Change Management
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<span class="mr-2 text-primary">→</span> Strategic Partnerships
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-center">
									<span class="mr-2 text-primary">→</span> Data (Modeling, Analytics, Architecture)
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div>
							<p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">
								Technical Stack
							</p>
							<div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span
									class="rounded bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-700"
									>R (tidyverse)</span
								>
								<span
									class="rounded bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-700"
									>Python</span
								>
								<span
									class="rounded bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-700"
									>Salesforce</span
								>
								<span
									class="rounded bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-700"
									>SQL</span
								>
								<span
									class="rounded bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-neutral-700"
									>Astro</span
								>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div>
							<p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">
								The Edge
							</p>
							<p class="mt-2 text-base font-medium text-neutral-800">
								Certified CrossFit Trainer <br />(CF-L3)
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</aside>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
